{"tid":625114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：「禁每日150單程證人士到港解房屋問題」不切實際","createTime":"2018-04-11T07:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:55:14.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":521,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"fd407ec93edafe80528542bd53306f291d30d0cf","tid":625114,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭：「禁每日150單程證人士到港解房屋問題」不切實際&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180411/s00001/01f08bbbf8924c4b7532fe6d8fb5208a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180411%2Fs00001%2F01f08bbbf8924c4b7532fe6d8fb5208a.jpg&h=4593af71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席立法會答問時指，房屋問題是今屆政府重中之重。但她批評有人說「禁止每日150名持單程證人士到港」便可解決房屋問題，是不切實際、混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強調，房屋供應量近年持續下降，唯有大量開拓土地，才能回應市民期盼。<br />\n<br />\n至於立法會房屋事務委員會昨通過要求房委會，全面檢討資助出售房屋售價，包括居屋及綠置居，並建議以成本價出售，林鄭月娥稱「好願意去看這個問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180411/s00001/1523427959708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180411%2Fs00001%2F1523427959708&d=e9b57mX1U%2F8HESOwWlL%2FBf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=eff29c31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180411%2Fs00001%2F1523427959708&h=8f407b28\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180411/s00001/1523427959708</a>"},{"pid":"a369a89571055928a90e36b89a27e797affa466f","tid":625114,"uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c50d9d99aa466acae44a04176e345b10dfc274f","tid":625114,"uid":85564,"like":156,"dislike":0,"score":156,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-